{"id":698,"date":"2024-11-14T14:49:00","date_gmt":"2024-11-14T20:49:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/?p=698"},"modified":"2025-12-09T14:50:29","modified_gmt":"2025-12-09T20:50:29","slug":"delta-tau-delta","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/posts\/2024\/2024\/delta-tau-delta\/","title":{"rendered":"Delta Tau Delta"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>This is part of the <a href=\"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/hazing-transparency-report\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"918\">Hazing Transparency Report<\/a>, which contains <a href=\"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/hazing-transparency-report\/#terminology\">terminology definitions<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/hazing-transparency-report\/#rules\">rules defined<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-style-elevated is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading alignwide\">Fall 2024<\/h2>\n\n\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper  \"><div class=\"ua_layout--grid\" >\n<div  >\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Incident: August &#8211; September 2024<br>Location: On Campus\/Off-Campus<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Reported: 11\/14\/2024<br>Reported by: Anonymous Report, Students, Staff<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Investigation: GSU Led<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Description<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Delta Tau Delta members forced\/coerced new members to purchase and consume alcohol. New members were subjected to line-ups, physical exercises and degrading activities. New members were subjected to phone confiscation\/controlled use and acts of personal servitude.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper  \"><div class=\"ua_layout--grid\" >\n<div  >\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Rules Violations<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Article III.B.(2)a. &#8211; Hazing<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Article III.B.(2)b. \u2013 Hazing Policy<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Article III.A.(4) &#8211; Published Policies<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Findings<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Hazing: Forced, coerced or intimidated consumption of alcohol in excess, actions intended to demean or embarrass, degradation, emotional harm, intimidation, lineups, phone confiscation, personal servitude.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Individuals Responsible: 7<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Arrests<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>None<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sanctions<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Disciplinary Probation from 1\/31\/2025 until 1\/30\/2026<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Loss of all Social Privileges through 5\/2\/2025<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Decreased Social Privileges &#8211; Fall 2025 (6 events)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Required co-host for hazing prevention speaker for IFC community &#8211; Fall 2025&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Required Hazing Prevention Presentation \u2013 Spring 2025&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Education Assessment Fee&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Chapter Hazing Education&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Executive Officer Training&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Establishment of Harm and Risk Reduction Committee&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Establishment of Alumni Advisory Board&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>National Headquarters sanctions&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Fall 2024 Description Delta Tau Delta members forced\/coerced new members to purchase and consume alcohol. New members were subjected to line-ups, physical exercises and degrading activities. New members were subjected to phone confiscation\/controlled use and acts of personal servitude.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{